OL,3,CFive women plan to pursue legal claim
OL,4,Cagainst Mohamed Al Fayed's estate
OL,6,FFive women who allege they were abused
OL,7,Fby Mohamed Al Fayed have said they are
OL,8,Fplanning to launch a legal claim for
OL,9,Fpersonal injury against the late
OL,10,Fbillionaire's estate.
OL,12,FLaw firm Leigh Day, which represents
OL,13,Fthe claimants, said a pre-action
OL,14,Fletter has been sent to lawyers for
OL,15,Fthe estate on behalf of the women, who
OL,16,Fworked as nannies and private air
OL,17,Fstewards for the former Harrods boss
OL,18,Fbetween 1995 and 2012.
